  h2 Basic
  p Use a simple
    span.class bg
    span.class sm-#
    | classes to code up the block grid and specify the number of items in a row.
  .rw
    .cl.md-6
      h4 HTML
      pre
        code(data-language="html").
          <ul class="bg sm-3">
            <li><!-- Your content goes here --></li>
            <li><!-- Your content goes here --></li>
            <li><!-- Your content goes here --></li>
